280
00:21:45,785 --> 00:21:47,505
I have an important thing to talk with him.

281
00:21:48,955 --> 00:21:50,370
I'll try.

282
00:21:56,629 --> 00:21:59,979
Tanya is self-willed.

283
00:22:01,888 --> 00:22:03,396
