328
00:24:52,310 --> 00:24:55,718
Your mom said you feel exhausted from work lately.

329
00:24:59,416 --> 00:25:00,416
No.

330
00:25:00,696 --> 00:25:02,596
My mom is too worried about me.

331
00:25:02,597 --> 00:25:03,811
